headline: Jeff Braun Reappointed as Allegion General Counsel
summary: DUBLIN, November 12, 2024--Allegion plc (NYSE: ALLE) a leading global security products and solutions provider, has reappointed Jeff Braun as senior vice president, general counsel and corporate secretary.
